<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well here is the scoop: his spawn time is 24min (varies from time to time), Golden Efreeti Boots are common drop and the Ring is rare. It has become alot easier to reach the Efreeti Lord, and yet it still takes about 12 people. The room can be easily held by about 3 or 4 people (only 3 spawns near and in room). If you plan on camping the efreeti I suggest you have a good enchanter at hand for imps hit for 120ish and the Efreeti has some nasty AE spells including Gravity Flux. And to a poor person I ran into, well rather the corpse, DONT CAMP IN EFREETI ROOM - it will be your downfall... Good luck and enjoy the many boots that will drop on your stay...</font></td></tr></table>
