<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I was on an Efreeti raid early today. It went along typically, we had two full groups of 45+'s. Everything went like clockwork till we realized that the latest patch had stepped up all the spawn rates. We'd take out 3 imps, go down the hallway a little farther and take out 2 more, only to have the other three pop up right behind us. Amazingly enough we didn't have an casualties the entire camp. The Efreeti himself is a pain in the ass to kill, he's got way too many hitpoints to boot, he's not lethal just annoying. His little imps aren't any better hit point wise, they just don't wanna die. Best of luck to all of those heading in his direction.</font></td></tr></table>
